author: Nick Baumgardner | nbaumgardner@mlive.com
title: Deadspin gets Jim Harbaugh's expense receipts, finds standard results
text: Every college coach in America goes through the process of filling out expense reports. Jim Harbaugh's no different. Well, he's Jim Harbaugh. Which might be the reason why Deadspin used Freedom of Information Requests to gain access to every expense...
